These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, singing, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family, mystery
4 different games are played: snooker, mah-jongg, domino, whist
House: cape-cod, wooden, craftsman, ranch-style
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8
 2. the cape-cod house is not to the left of the cape-cod house##8
 3. the ranch-style house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person playing snooker is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
 5. the cape-cod house is not to the right of the cape-cod house##8
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 7. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the wooden house and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 9. the ranch-style house is the person watching family movies##1
10. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##5
13. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the ranch-style house##8
14. the person who's hobby is dancing is the craftsman house##1
15. the person who's hobby is dancing is not the person playing mah-jongg##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | camping     | dancing   | woodworking | singing |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| Game         | mah-jongg  | domino  | whist  | snooker |
| House     | cape-cod    | craftsman | wooden     | ranch-style    |

