.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, milk, sprite, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, spy, disaster, martial-arts
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, aquamarine, grey, orange
 1. the fan of salsa is between the person who likes azure and the fan of indie##2
 2. the person drinking milk is not to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##8
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the person who likes orange##8
 5. the person who likes azure is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
 7. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the person who likes orange##5
 8. the person who likes grey is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the person who likes aquamarine##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who likes azure##3
11. the person who likes azure is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
17. the person drinking lemonade is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person watching spy movies is not to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##8
19. the person drinking water is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | sprite | water  | milk  |
| Movie-Genre          | martial-arts     | spy | musical | disaster  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
| Color           | grey | orange | azure    | aquamarine  |

