 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person playing billiard##8
 7. the fan of folk is in an odd position##4
 8. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing chess##1
 9. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing domino##1
10. the electrician is on the far right##1
11. the person playing mah-jongg is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8
12. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the electrician##3

.:: Answer ::.
