 6. the colonial house is not to the right of the dutch##8
 7. the craftsman house is not the thai##6
 8. the person eating grapes is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the craftsman house##7
 9. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapes##5
10. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
11. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
12. the person eating grapes is not the argentine##6
13. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
14. the wooden house is on the left of the colonial house##1
15. the person driving the bus is not to the right of the person eating grapes##8

