.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-16::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, lilac, grey, azure
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, chaman, alhambra, swisher
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, lacrosse, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the person who likes grey is the person who's sport is tennis##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person who likes lilac is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
 7. the person who likes lilac is on the left or right of the person who likes grey##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the person who likes lilac is not to the right of the chaman-smoker##8
11. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Color      | orange   | azure     | grey    | lilac |
| Cigar   | dunhill  | swisher      | alhambra     | chaman     |
| Sport         | climbing | lacrosse  | tennis     | cycling  |
| Transport     | bike     | quad-bike | snowmobile | boat     |

