.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, soccer, rugby, sailing
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, doctor, social-worker, teacher
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, ivory, grey, red
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, jazz, reggae
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the left of the bartender##8
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
 3. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the right of the fan of jazz##5
 4. the teacher is the person who likes red##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is not the social-worker##6
 6. the person who likes lavender is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
 7. the person who likes ivory is not to the left of the social-worker##8
 8. the social-worker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 9. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
10. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
11. the person who likes lavender is in an even position##4
12. the person who's sport is rugby is between the social-worker and the person who's sport is sailing##2
13. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |       3       |     4      |
